text: Caan (als: Caan van Neck and De la Bassecour Caan) was the name of a Dutch patrician family. == History == The oldest known family member Heynderick Thielemans (Caen), a baker in Delfshaven who died in 1644. ==Bibliography == *Nederland's Patriciaat 16 (1926), p. 37-45. Category:Dutch patrician families
title: Caan (Dutch family)
